Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the Pony Post?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was just you, Opal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Every other day he's\Nhere like clockwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But not today! What could\Npossibly be holding him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Strawberry Cinnamon\NCilantro Salutations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're wondering what\Nwarrants such a welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that welcome is warranted\Nby a pony that whisked up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a warm batch of Strawberry\NCinnamon Cilantro cupcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That strangely sickening\Nflavor combination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,sounds just as bad as it tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came here to\Noffer you some!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After that visually descriptive\Nand disturbing endorsement,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I almost forgot! I have\Nthis letter for you, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Post Pony was\Ngoing to deliver it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but after his Strawberry\NCinnamon Cilantro cupcake,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he was feeling kind of queasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And since I was\Nheading over anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I could do it\Nfor him. There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I GOT IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,WOO HOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been holding out\Nfor the perfect location
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and it finally became available.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I can fulfill my dream of\NOPENING A BOUTIQUE IN CANTERLOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M SO EXCITED, I THINK I'M\NGOING TO LOSE MY CUPCAKES!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity's such a\Nsavvy business pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so impressed she used\Nthe huge bonus she earned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,making the costumes for Sapphire\NShores' Equestria-wide tour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to open this\Nsecond boutique!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it from your reaction\Nthat you like the boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Rarity, I know\Nhard work when I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and it looks like you worked\Nyour hooves to the nub.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Those hooves don't\Nlook nubby. They look scrubbied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And buffied. And pedied!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, despite my nubby,\Nscrubby, buffy pony pedi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually have been\Nworking very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I never could have\Ngotten the boutique ready
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Grand Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,without the help of my new\Nmanager: Sassy Saddles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bust my buttons, Rarity!\NThe Ponies from Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I needed a manager\Nfor Canterlot Carousel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So when Sassy showed\Nme her resume and I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that she'd worked in all the\Nfinest boutiques in Canterlot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hired her right\Non the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I then laid out this\Nplan or "pattern"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,as we say in the fashion\Nbiz, for Canterlot Carousel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so that Rarity's boutique\Nwill be a guaranteed success
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and those doors will\Nnever, ever, ever close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Sassy, your attention to\Ndetail is truly impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already put a pin in the\Nfirst piece of the pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beautify the Boutique."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But next was the very\Ncrucial pattern piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Marketing to the Mares."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out that everypony\Nhere loves royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I created a collection that\Nbeautifully revolves around
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the royal element of Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just so happens there's a\Nhot new princess in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In every poll\NSassy Saddles took,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you were the most\Npopular Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Coincidentally, one of my gowns\Nis inspired by the window
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in Canterlot Castle\Ncommemorating your coronation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,While I've always prided myself\Non paying attention to detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken my latest collection\Nto a whole new level
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,with Rarity's Rules of TLC.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by this baby, TLC stands\Nfor Tasty Licorice Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,TLC stands for Time,\NLove, and Couture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I do agree that\Nthis dress has potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not had enough Time\Nto give it enough Love
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to become Couture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But the rest of the\Ngowns in tonight's line
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,have met Rarity's Rules and\Nare ready to be presented!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My marketing research also\Nconfirmed that customers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that viewed somepony\Nfamous wearing a gown
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,wished to own that\Ngown for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I call this piece of the\Npattern "Celebrity Status."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Twilight, we were\Nwondering if perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you might possibly\Nwear this tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If being a Princess\Nand wearing that dress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,can help your boutique\Nin any way, then I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick a pin in it! It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everypony!\NLet's set the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a little filly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all I've ever wanted was to own\Na boutique here in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony pinch me, I'm\Nabout to open the doors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to that very boutique!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Grand Opening\Nof Canterlot Carousel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello! Nice to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, welcome! Oh, I'm\Nso happy you could make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That Sassy totally stepped\Non your hooves, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Did she mess\Nup that nice pony pedi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't think she meant to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity. Are you ready to\Nreveal the collection?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she sure she doesn't\Nwant to do it herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am. Fluttershy. Could\Nyou help Twilight get ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fillies and Gentlecolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am designer and\Ncouturier, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to\Nwelcome you again
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Grand Opening\Nof Canterlot Carousel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am thrilled that\Nyou're here to see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,my newest collection\Ninspired by this regal city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fashion Plate of\NCosmare Magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so honored that Cosmare\Nwas able to do a piece
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Grand Opening\Nof my boutique!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when Sassy Saddles\Ncalls saying she's found
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the latest and\Ngreatest in fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we high tail without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now tell me all about\Nyour latest collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, uh. It's called\NRarity's Royal Regalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Royally radiant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite part\Nof being a designer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is finding my inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And that really wasn't difficult\Nwhen it came to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere I looked, the\Nroyal city just spoke to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it, "In-Spire-ation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Genius! Simply genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent hours by the lily\Npond on the castle grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which inspired this\Ngown, "Water Filly."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the whimsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching Celestia raise\Nthe sun each morning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,literally lit up my day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is "Tripping the Light!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, Luna raising\Nthe moon guided me to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I call this, "Over the Moon."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I certainly am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And for our finale, I have\Nsomething very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was inspired by the\Nstained glass window
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,created in honor of\NPrincess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So I call this, "The\NReign in Stain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the dress is\Ninspired by the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,stained glass window\Nof a reigning Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think "The\NReign in Stain"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is too difficult\Nto explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially for the signature\Npiece of a collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I rather like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fillies and Gentlecolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Sassy Saddles, am\Npleased to introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the Grand Finale of\Nthe Grand Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of Rarity's Royal Regalia!\N"The Princess Dress!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony! Please follow me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can all place your\Norders for...The Princess Dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, I want to be the first\Npony to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess Dress\Nhas just guaranteed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Canterlot Carousel's success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Rarity's Royal\NRegalia is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And everypony seemed to\Nlove the Princess Dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet your saddle they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity now has one hundred\Norders for her signature gown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred\Norders? All at one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my pattern,\Nthe next piece is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Success of The\NSignature Dress!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I do not see the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cupcake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, Sassy Saddles,\NI would have appreciated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,getting to name the final gown\Nfrom my collection myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My research shows that\Nyour "Reign in Stain" name
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,was a play on words that\Nwas both very confusing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and quite unappealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,While I see your point, we\Nshould have discussed it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to the Grand\NOpening, Sassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My only goal is for Canterlot\NCarousel to succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I changed the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is why I took all those\Norders for the Princess Dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But receiving orders for one\Nhundred dresses in one day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is just too much too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you actually saying we\Nshould cancel these orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:11:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Sassy. Promises were made\Nand I shall sew my very best
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to provide each and every pony\Na Princess Dress full of TLC!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you,\NRarity! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, satin and silk, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want\Nyour friends to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,make the dresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Sassy. These orders\Nare my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do\Nis stick to my plan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can deliver each\Nand every Princess Dress
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in keeping with my\NRules of Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The Rules of Rarity{\i0}\N{\i1} Guaranteed Quality! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ This I can assure! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ For each and every dress{\i0}\N{\i1} I vow to give finesse ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ With Time, Love, and Couture ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ My favorite moment's{\i0}\N{\i1} when a pony sees it. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That special gown{\i0}\N{\i1} that she just adores ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That pony's now in style!{\i0}\N{\i1}My hard work's all worthwhile ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Oh, yes, it makes my{\i0}\N{\i1} heart, my heart, just soar! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The Rules of Rarity{\i0}\N{\i1} Just a parody ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ No dress here's unique{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The panels all the same{\i0}\N{\i1} Each colored window pane ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ My fashion only makes{\i0}\N{\i1} me want to shriek! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Oh, to create! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Would give me elation! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ To feel once again{\i0}\N{\i1} some inspiration! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Come on now, Rarity!{\i0}\N{\i1} Give me some clarity ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Time for your{\i0}\N{\i1} couture love to rule! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The Rules of Rarity!{\i0}\N{\i1} Extra TLC ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ This feels more sublime! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Soon now they will see{\i0}\N{\i1} how good these can be ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ with a little extra shine! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The Rules of Rarity!{\i0}\N{\i1} Guaranteed Quality! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ All can see it's true! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ These new gems add such flare{\i0}\N{\i1} Their beauty can't compare ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ This old style{\i0}\N{\i1} suddenly gleams anew! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the customer who\Nordered this Princess Dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of\Nher. You keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, actually, I'd love\Nto see her reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to this particular dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Paisley and Poplin, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the orders\Nyou still have to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to\Ntake a break? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just...I made\Nsome really lovely changes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to this dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But every Princess Dress is\Nsupposed to be exactly the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I know. But these\Ngems just spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Go see her reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, and welcome to\NCanterlot Carousel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so pleased to\Npresent to you your...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,PRINCESS DRESS! Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been simply\Ndesperate to get this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since I saw Princess\NTwilight wearing it at your...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. There's\Nsomething different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as an artiste,\NI did take the liberty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to change a few minor details.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I...I saw these gems\Nglistening in the light
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and they just spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they lovely?\NAnd so unique?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fine. But they're not\Nwhat I ordered, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...no, they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the dress to be\Nexactly like the one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight\Nwore. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The Rules of Rarity{\i0}\N{\i1} Once stood for something ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But now it feels just{\i0}\N{\i1} like some factory ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Now every dress I make{\i0}\N{\i1} With every flaw and mistake ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:16:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Oh, how it makes my heart,{\i0}\N{\i1} my heart, just break! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Raving ricrac, Rarity! You made\Ntwo hundred Princess Dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Isn't it spectacular?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a special\Nsurprise for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The latest issue of Cosmare\NMagazine just hit the stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Canterlot's\NNewest Rising Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the hour since\Nthe magazine's come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we've gotten another hundred new\Norders for the Princess Dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One...hundred...more...\NPrincess Dresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Cosmare Coverpony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the most successful\Nshop in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:17:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten everything I ever\Nwanted, but...I'm...miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you\Npossibly be miserable?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My pattern is perfect.\N"COSMARE COVERPONY!" Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your signature gown!\N"THE PRINCESS DRESS: A SUCCESS!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make another\Nhundred Princess Dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a piece for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"ASSEMBLE THE ASSEMBLY LINE!"\NYou'll never have to sew again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Then the "CANTERLOT\NCAROUSEL NEVER CLOSES!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and "SASSY SADDLES'\NBOUTIQUE SUCCEEDS!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! This is not\Nyour boutique!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if this is what success\Nin Canterlot looks like,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want no part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, make up flyers for a\NGoing Out of Business Sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm closing\NCanterlot Carousel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No! Oh, you\Ncan't, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked too hard\Nto make this a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be a part of...\NANOTHER FAILED BOUTIQUE!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you look lovely! Nice\Nto see you out here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems Sassy Saddles\Nisn't rushing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to open the door\Nthis time. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Going\NOut of Business Sale
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of Canterlot Carousel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this Princess\NDress on sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry, the Princess\NDress has been discontinued.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are plenty of other\Nlovely dresses on sale today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. This dress completely\Nspeaks to my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly! The dressing\Narea is right back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most amazing\Nof amazing dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at it\Nbrightens my day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure you'll feel even\Nbrighter once you try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have this\NIn-Spire-ation dress
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that's in the new\Nissue of Cosmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I do! It's right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bats in the belfry!\NI have to try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this dress makes\Nme feel like a Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this dress makes me\Nfeel like a Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This gown is quite beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but it totally clashes\Nwith my complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Perhaps you'd be even\Nmore taken with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was inspired by the fountain\Nin the Canterlot Castle Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it, "The\NFountain of Truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly what\NI've been dreaming of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Well, then, I'll finish it\Nand the gown shall be yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I've\Nbeen dreaming about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ My favorite moment's{\i0}\N{\i1} when a pony sees it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That special gown{\i0}\N{\i1} that she just adores ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That pony's now in style{\i0}\N{\i1}My hard work's all worthwhile ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Oh, yes, it makes my{\i0}\N{\i1} heart, my heart, just soar! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention everypony! Canterlot\NCarousel WILL NOT be closing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But this stuff's\Nstill on sale, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity,\NI'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I focused on that\None dress
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rest of Rarity's\NRoyal Regalia paid the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so did the\NPrincess Dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I sewed, the\Nmore each dress lost its
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, Love, and Couture becoming\NTerrible, Lackluster and Common.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I finally understand\Nthe Rules of Rarity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and will apply them\Nat my next job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rules of Rarity\Nare only to be applied
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,at Canterlot Carousel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why you must continue\Nto manage the boutique
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:20:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,while I'm in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, I'll come to\NCanterlot with new designs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and to see the\Ncustomers, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but Ponyville was always\Ngoing to be my home base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bobbins and\Nbodkins, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you,\Nthank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I promise to run everything\Nfollowing your rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I would expect\Nnothing less!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,OH MY GOSH! A SALE?! DO YOU\NHAVE THAT PRINCESS DRESS?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
